SELECT [m].[Product_id], [m].[Product_name], [m].[Product_category_id], [m].[Sell_price], [m].[Sale_price], [m].[Product_vat], [m].[Unit_id], [m].[IsAvailable], [m].[Status], CASE
    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [Product_image] AS [p]
        WHERE [m].[Product_id] = [p].[Product_id]) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [t0].[Product_image_id], [t0].[Product_id], [t0].[Product_image]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t].[Product_image_id], [t].[Product_id], [t].[Product_image]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p0].[Product_image_id], [p0].[Product_id], [p0].[Product_image], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [p0].[Product_id] ORDER BY [p0].[Product_image_id]) AS [row]
        FROM [Product_image] AS [p0]
    ) AS [t]
    WHERE [t].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [m].[Product_id] = [t0].[Product_id]
WHERE ([m].[IsDelete] = CAST(0 AS bit)) OR ([m].[IsDelete] IS NULL)
ORDER BY [m].[Product_name]
2025-04-13 17:24:43.833 +07:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (10ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [m].[Product_id], [m].[Product_name], [m].[Product_category_id], [m].[Sell_price], [m].[Sale_price], [m].[Product_vat], [m].[Unit_id], [m].[IsAvailable], [m].[Status], CASE
    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [Product_image] AS [p]
        WHERE [m].[Product_id] = [p].[Product_id]) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [t0].[Product_image_id], [t0].[Product_id], [t0].[Product_image]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t].[Product_image_id], [t].[Product_id], [t].[Product_image]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p0].[Product_image_id], [p0].[Product_id], [p0].[Product_image], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [p0].[Product_id] ORDER BY [p0].[Product_image_id]) AS [row]
        FROM [Product_image] AS [p0]
    ) AS [t]
    WHERE [t].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [m].[Product_id] = [t0].[Product_id]
WHERE ([m].[IsDelete] = CAST(0 AS bit)) AND ([m].[Status] = CAST(1 AS bit))
ORDER BY [m].[Product_name]

    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [Product_image] AS [p]
        WHERE [m].[Product_id] = [p].[Product_id]) THEN CAST(1 AS bit)
    ELSE CAST(0 AS bit)
END, [t0].[Product_image_id], [t0].[Product_id], [t0].[Product_image]
FROM [Menu] AS [m]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [t].[Product_image_id], [t].[Product_id], [t].[Product_image]
    FROM (
        SELECT [p0].[Product_image_id], [p0].[Product_id], [p0].[Product_image], ROW_NUMBER() OVER(PARTITION BY [p0].[Product_id] ORDER BY [p0].[Product_image_id]) AS [row]
        FROM [Product_image] AS [p0]
    ) AS [t]
    WHERE [t].[row] <= 1
) AS [t0] ON [m].[Product_id] = [t0].[Product_id]
WHERE ([m].[IsDelete] = CAST(0 AS bit)) AND ([m].[Status] = CAST(1 AS bit))
ORDER BY [m].[Product_name]

SELECT [u].[User_id], [u].[create_date], [u].[email], [u].[isDelete], [u].[is_verify], [u].[password], [u].[phone], [u].[role_id], [u].[status], [u].[user_information_id], [u0].[User_information_id], [u0].[Address], [u0].[Date_of_birth], [u0].[District], [u0].[Province_City], [u0].[User_name], [u0].[Ward_Commune], [o].[Order_id], [o].[Amount_due], [o].[Created_time], [o].[Customer_id], [o].[Delivery_information_id], [o].[Order_note], [o].[Order_status_id], [o].[Order_type_id], [o].[Room_id], [o].[Shipper_id], [o].[Total_quantity]
FROM [User] AS [u]
